             was indicted for <rs id="t18020428-12-off58" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18020428-12-off58" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18020428-12-off58" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18020428-12-cd59" type="crimeDate">1st of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020428-12-off58 t18020428-12-cd59"></join>, thirty yards of linen cloth, value 30s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t18020428-12-victim100" type="victimName">
                  Thomas 
                  Knight
               <interp inst="t18020428-12-victim100" type="surname" value="Knight"></interp>
